{
  "stem": "1183.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I got a kiss through the barbed wire from him, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he, that third time, he was able to save my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Also, on the other side when some, some comic things, more or less.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was still-- there was some theater, and some entertainment was sometimes going on in Vught.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I don't think I attended that, but I heard about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Kids were singing and-- at that time, and the kids were still there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there are some songs that sometimes they sing, and if I hear them, I cringe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember, though, those kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There also, the funny part, the comic part is that they had put on the barbed wire bottles, and glass, and bells.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So why?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because still, although they put some stuff in the food that inhibits the, the-- Sexual desire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--sexual desires, it didn't work so apparently for some men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they tried over to climb the barbed wire, and went into the women's barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when you knew that-- I mean, I was a child still, but still, when you heard the clinking, you knew that someone's trying to get in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think quite a couple succeeded, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the semi-comic part of, of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on Sundays we were allowed visits in the beginning, from the men visited the children, or the husbands visited the wives.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was still allowed in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now then I started to work with Philips, and it was come some [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] flashlights, but primitive flashlights, what you move with your hand, and then that produces the lights.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No clue how it is in English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's what I-- that they made on the assembly line.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
